      <title>约旦以地区风险为由暂时关闭领空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/jordan-temporarily-closes-airspace-citing-regional-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国营的 Al Mamlaka 通讯社报道，约旦周六暂时对进出、出境和过境航班关闭领空，理由是该地区的风险日益增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/jordan-temporarily-closes-airspace-citing-regional-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 19:35:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登重返白宫处理中东事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/biden-returning-to-white-house-to-deal-with-middle-east-events</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将返回白宫，与他的国家安全团队就中东事件进行磋商，缩短他在特拉华州私人住宅的周末时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/biden-returning-to-white-house-to-deal-with-middle-east-events</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 17:21:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>脆弱的钢铁之州民主党人敦促拜登停止日本交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/vulnerable-steel-state-democrats-press-biden-to-stop-nippon-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名处于艰难连任斗争中的钢铁州民主党人敦促总统乔·拜登采取更多措施，阻止日本新日铁公司收购美国钢铁公司的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-13/vulnerable-steel-state-democrats-press-biden-to-stop-nippon-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
